works.description: BMW has used this year’s Concorso d’Eleganza Villa d’Este event in Italy to mark the 75th anniversary of the original BMW 328 classic of the late 1930s by displaying the BMW 328 Hommage concept car. Karl Bäumer, CEO of BMW Group Classic, said that with the BMW 328 Hommage, they wish to pay homage to the passion and inventiveness of the fathers of the BMW 328.
